query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'gaming',
'security',
'webmasters')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('encryption',
'minecraft',
'organic-chemistry',
'seo')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Constituent',
'Curious',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Good Question',
'Guru',
'Informed',
'Reviewer',
'Scholar',
'Suffrage',
'Tag Editor') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
